result.name: great-yarmouth-south-denes-enterprise-zone
result.notes: The Enterprise Zones were created in April 2012 to encourage offshore energy, port and logistics activity in both the South Denes (Great Yarmouth) and Beacon Park (Gorleston) commercial areas of the borough. They benefit from time limited business rate relief, a simplified planning process and superfast broadband.
